description:
For ya’ll who haven’t played this game - it's basically about virus outbreak that sweeps the whole world. Just let that sink in... Gamers have also been startled to discover that there is a biological research lab near the city where the outbreak originated has a familiar logo. Shanghai Ruilan Bao Hu San Biotech Limited seems to be linked to the Umbrella Corporation from Resident Evil.
It has also been pointed out that Corona is an anagram of ‘Racoon’, fans of Resident Evil will know that the original outbreak in the game started in Raccoon city.
